---
// Fundations
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<section class="bg-[#111110]">
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-24">
    <div
      class="max-w-prose"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="2000"
    >
      <p class="font-sans font-light text-lg leading-relaxed text-base-400">
        Founders usually come to us with something specific in mind — a dashboard, a workflow tool, a product feature. They've already decided what needs to be built.
      </p>

      <p class="font-display text-2xl leading-snug text-[#f0ede8] my-12">
        Your biggest AI opportunity probably isn't what you think it is.
      </p>

      <p class="font-sans font-light text-lg leading-relaxed text-base-400 mb-10">
        That's not a knock on how founders think. It's just that the highest-leverage moment in a business is rarely obvious from the inside. It's buried in a workflow nobody questions, a dataset nobody's using, a handoff that bleeds hours every week. You can't see it clearly when you're running the company.
      </p>

      <p class="font-sans font-light text-lg leading-relaxed text-base-400">
        That's what we do first. Before we design anything, before we write a line of code — we find it. Then we build it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
</section>
